<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>Admission & School Rules | Information Hub</title>
  <!-- Google Fonts + Font Awesome 6 -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,500;14..32,600;14..32,700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/school/css/admission1.css">
 
</head>
<body>
     <%- include("partials/navbar.ejs") %>
<div class="page-container">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1><i class="fas fa-school"></i> Admission & School Rules</h1>
    <div class="header-shine"></div>
    <div class="subhead">Your complete guide to admission process, daily schedule, dress code & policies</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Information Card -->
  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="card-inner">
      <!-- LEFT PANEL: Admission Procedure + Fee -->
      <div class="panel left-panel">
        <div class="section-title">
          <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i> 
          <span>Admission Procedure</span>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: #3e5c66;">For admission, guardian needs to contact the office on working days with the required documents.</p>
        
        <div class="doc-list">
          <p><i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i> Documents Required:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Two passport size photos</li>
            <li>Birth certificate copy</li>
            <li>Last school transfer certificate</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <ul class="procedure-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Once all documents and completely filled form are submitted, test date and time are provided.</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Admission is based on the test performance of the individual.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="fee-box" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">
            <i class="fas fa-rupee-sign" style="color:#e0a158;"></i>
            <h4 style="font-weight: 700; color:#2a5f6b;">Fee Structure</h4>
          </div>
          <p>For detailed fee structure (tuition, development, transport, etc.), please refer to the school office or download the prospectus.</p>
          <div class="fee-note">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Fee concession available for meritorious & economically weaker sections as per board norms.
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="#" class="btn-contact"><i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Enquiry / Contact Admission Cell</a>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT PANEL: General Rules, Timings, Dress Code, Conveyance -->
      <div class="panel right-panel">
        <div class="section-title">
          <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
          <span>School Bell Timing</span>
        </div>
        <div class="timing-grid">
          <div class="timing-item">
            <span class="timing-category"><i class="fas fa-child"></i> Pre-Primary</span>
            <span class="timing-value">9:00 AM to 12:50 PM</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timing-item">
            <span class="timing-category"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i> Class I to X</span>
            <span class="timing-value">8:10 AM to 2:10 PM</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          <i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i>
          <span>Dress Code</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="dress-grid">
          <div class="dress-card">
            <div class="dress-day"><i class="far fa-calendar-alt"></i> Monday / Tuesday / Thursday / Friday</div>
            <div class="dress-desc"><strong>Boys:</strong> Yellow shirt and oxford blue trouser &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Girls:</strong> Yellow shirt and oxford blue skirt</div>
          </div>
          <div class="dress-card">
            <div class="dress-day"><i class="fas fa-flag-checkered"></i> Wednesday / Saturday</div>
            <div class="dress-desc"><strong>Boys:</strong> White house wise T-shirt and white trouser &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Girls:</strong> White house wise T-shirt and white skirt</div>
            <span class="badge-icon">House wise</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="small-note"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Students must wear neatly ironed uniforms with identity card. Sports uniform on designated PT days.</p>

        <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          <i class="fas fa-bus"></i>
          <span>Conveyance</span>
        </div>
        <div class="conveyance-box">
          <p><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color:#e0a158;"></i> Conveyance facility is available from all parts of the city.</p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-hand-peace"></i> Conveyance facility is optional, parents may enroll for it.</p>
          <p class="small-note" style="margin-top: 8px;"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> School is not responsible for any liability regarding conveyance.</p>
        </div>

        <hr>
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: space-between;">
          <div><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt" style="color:#e0a158;"></i> Admission office open: Mon-Fri (9 AM – 3 PM)</div>
          <div><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +91-11-40802345</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Additional note / footer links -->
  <div class="footer-note">
    <i class="fas fa-gavel"></i> All rules are subject to periodic updates. For any clarification, kindly contact the administrative office.  
    <a href="#" style="color:#b55a1a; text-decoration: none;">Download admission form →</a>
  </div>
</div>
<%-include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
</body>
</html>